cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this model personality analysis corpus, please cite it as below."
title: "Model Personality Analysis Corpus"
abstract: >
  A derived qualitative analysis corpus for studying model personality and
  posture across frontier LLMs, built on the Convergent Form, Divergent Voice II
  raw trace corpus. Includes per-sample freeflow personality/vibe readings,
  per-model personality profiles and cards, values-probe summaries, taxonomy
  tables, route/provider difference reports, methodology notes, and
  website-bundled copies of raw samples for browsing and audit.
